## Context
Brief context from parent goal...

## Problem Statement
What needs to be solved...

## Technology Considerations
### Option 1: Technology A
- Pros: ...
- Cons: ...

### Option 2: Technology B
- Pros: ...
- Cons: ...

### Decision: Chosen Technology
Rationale for choice...

## Implementation Hints

